== 鐵路 ==
[[File:ZCG461_Virpazar.jpg|thumb]]上。]]
蒙特內哥罗最早的铁路于1901年由[[奥匈帝国|奥匈帝国]]在其属地[[科托尔湾|科托尔湾]]修筑，但是第一条由[[蒙特內哥罗王国|蒙特內哥罗政府]]修筑的铁路于1905年开工，1908年通车，它连接了蒙特內哥罗海港城市[[巴尔|巴尔]]和[[斯库台湖|斯库台湖]]边的{{link-en|维帕札|Virpazar}}。一战结束后，铁路线又从维帕札延伸至[[波德戈里察|波德戈里察]]，并最终在1970年代後期通至[[贝尔格莱德|贝尔格莱德]]，成为了[[貝爾格勒－巴爾鐵路|貝爾格勒－巴爾鐵路]]的一部分。其中，[[馬拉里耶卡高架橋|馬拉里耶卡高架橋]]自竣工至2001年也是世界最高的鐵路橋。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.serbiaconstruction.com/projects/the-mala-rijeka-bridge/ |title=Serbia Construction The Mala Rijeka bridge |access-date=2019-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170208040309/http://www.serbiaconstruction.com/projects/the-mala-rijeka-bridge/ |archive-date=2017-02-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://me.visit-montenegro.com/explore/central/virpazar/ |title=Virpazar, Visit Montenegro |access-date=2021-10-16 |archive-date=2021-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019042232/https://me.visit-montenegro.com/explore/central/virpazar/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.kolektiv.me/67950/foto-virpazar-mjesto-koje-vrijedi-posjetiti-u-svako-doba-godine-i-jednostavno-uivati |title=Virpazar: Mjesto koje vrijedi posjetiti u svako doba godine, i jednostavno uživati |access-date=2021-10-16 |archive-date=2020-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327211048/https://www.kolektiv.me/67950/foto-virpazar-mjesto-koje-vrijedi-posjetiti-u-svako-doba-godine-i-jednostavno-uivati |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.pobjeda.co.me/citanje.php?datum=2008-06-01&id=142257|title="Lovćen" se vraća kući|publisher=[[Pobjeda|Pobjeda]]|date=2008-01-06|access-date=2011-01-19|archive-date=2013-02-19|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130219030202/http://www.pobjeda.co.me/citanje.php?datum=2008-06-01&id=142257|dead-url=yes}}</ref>蒙特內哥羅國內鐵路總長度為250公里，全部為標準軌。该国主要有三条铁路，分别为[[貝爾格勒－巴爾鐵路|貝爾格勒－巴爾鐵路]]、{{link-ja|尼克希奇－波德戈里察鐵路|ニクシッチ＝ポドゴリツァ鉄道}}和通往阿尔巴尼亚的{{link-ja|波德戈里察－斯库台鐵路|ポドゴリツァ＝シュコドラ鉄道}}。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.t669.net/hekurudha_shqiptare.html |title=Hekurudha Shqiptare |author= |date= |work= |publisher= |language=sq |accessdate=31 August 2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402114036/http://www.t669.net/hekurudha_shqiptare.html |archive-date=2 April 2016 |url-status=dead }}</ref>其中，通往[[阿尔巴尼亚|阿尔巴尼亚]]的铁路曾经一度在[[南斯拉夫内战|南斯拉夫内战]]中遭到破坏，但已经于2003年恢复通车，蒙特內哥罗政府正在与阿尔巴尼亚政府讨论增加国际客运列车的方案。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.shkoder.net/en/news.htm |title=Shkoder-Bajze railway ready to operate for transportation of commodities |author=M. Malja |date=13 February 2003 |accessdate=31 August 2010 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140904012250/http://www.shkoder.net/en/news.htm |archivedate=4 September 2014 }}</ref>
